high_descs: Turn right from the hall and go straight towards the kitchen near to the countertop.
Open the door of the oven and pick the apple from the oven.
Turn right and take the apple towards the kitchen sink.
Wash the apple in the kitchen sink and then pick it from the sink.
Take the washed apple and head go nearby to the microwave.
Put the apple inside of the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Pick the apple from the microwave, wash it and put it in the oven.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the countertop.
Take out the apple from the microwave.
Turn left to reach the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink and take the apple out.
Turn right to reach the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Apple in the Microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, move straight towards the counter top.
Open the microwave, take the apple from inside, close the microwave.
Turn left, move right towards the sink.
Put the apple inside the sink, wash it, get back the apple.
Turn right, move left towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To get the apple from microwave, wash it in the sink, put back in the microwave.
